com.ibm.ccl.soa.deploy.core
Interface Agreement

All Known Subinterfaces:
ConfigurationContract, ExplicitContract, InstanceConfiguration
public interface Agreement

An agreement defines the public elements and public editable DeployModelObjects on a Topology.

Since:
1.0
See Also:
ConfigurationContract, InstanceConfiguration

Method Detail

getVisibleUnits

java.util.List<Unit> getVisibleUnits()
Returns the set of visible units from the referenced Topology. The returned set will include public units, as well as units that contain public children or exposed properties.

The list that is returned may not be modified.

Returns:
The set of visible units from the referenced Topology.
